item.description:
@chessy019 wrote:

yeah it does work but like matthew said you have to be admin or owner or co-owner (you get the point dont you?) and if you want to know how to type it in and get the item open up a www.moparisthebest.com and at top of screen it says “help” click help and under you should see “item id’s” click that and let it load…for an example say you want 2 easter rings ( DONT DO THIS I HEARD IT GIVES SERVER BUGS!) type the item id of easter rings and how many you want like this:
pickup::7928( item ID) 2(amount of how many you want)
And if you’ve done that correctly and have pickup enabled to your server it should work!!! Hope i helped

                          pm if you have anymore questions i'll be glad to help ANYONE.
